entries.s_c76aeb53: There is a village to the southeast that needs some help.  I do not have all the details.  I am sure if you talk to the village elder, all of your questions will be answered.  I must go.  Good luck to you.
entries.s_b46f1e5e: Hello, welcome to Dathomir.  I was told you would be looking for me.  Have you spoken to the village elder yet?
entries.s_827a56fe: Village elder? Please tell me more.
